Interface IPersistable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSet, Aggregation, DataAttribute, DomainModel, InputSet, OutputSet

    public interface IPersistable
    The Interface for database persistence. The Interface consists of a method, which allows the implementer to be saved in the database.
